To calculate molBV, which is the imputed continuous Nugent score, the log ratios between Lactobacillus and BV specific markers were generated (e.g., Lactobacillus:Prevotella, Lactobacillus:Gardnerella, Lactobacillus: Shuttleworthia, etc.) and used, along with the data from Supplementary Table 6, to calculate molBV:\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
